The outlet strip is held together with screws, thus allowing for easy disassembly and reassembly.  I loosely followed
[this article](https://web.archive.org/web/20220925232455/http://www.hagensieker.com/blog/page/?post_id=44&title=esp8266-hack-of-inexpensive-wifi-outlet)
for pinout guidance, as it is the same chip and logic board.
